## Week 8: Deployment (Vercel & Azure)
**Videos**
- Deploy Website on Vercel – https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nbNY3cT0dU0
- Deploy MERN Stack Frontend & Backend on Vercel – https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mhQWPV8GUDw
- How To Deploy on Vercel (Updated) – https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3izAncxuO78

**Copilot Prompts**
- `# vercel.json: generate config for Next.js with env vars and headers`
- `# CI/CD: GitHub Actions workflow to build & deploy on push to main`
- `# Troubleshooting: checklist for common Vercel build errors`
- `# Post‑deploy: script to run health checks & log metrics`

**Quiz**
1. Steps to deploy a Next.js app to Vercel with env vars.
2. CI/CD auto‑deploy setup.
3. Preview vs production on Vercel.
4. Custom domain + DNS.
5. Common build errors & fixes.
6. Zero‑downtime deployments.
7. Metrics/logs to check post‑deploy.
8. Secure secrets for build/runtime.
9. Static site vs Node backend on Vercel.
10. (Optional) Azure Static Web Apps outline.

