## Tips
- Keep snippets in separate files (`/snippets`) and link to them here.
- Use checkboxes to track progress:
  - [ ] Watch videos
  - [ ] Complete prompts
  - [ ] Pass quiz (≥8/10)
- Commit this file to a private Git repo for versioned notes.

